    "composer": "Adoniran Barbosa/Marcos César",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>                            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vila Esperança, foi lá que eu passei o meu primeiro carnaval</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F°\">F°</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vila Esperança, foi lá que eu conheci Maria Rosa, meu primeiro amor</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Como fui feliz, naquele fevereiro, pois tudo para mim era primeiro</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F°\">F°</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Primeira Rosa, primeira esperança, primeiro carnaval, primeiro amor criança</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Numa volta no salão ela me olhou eu envolvi seu corpo em serpentina</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>                                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E tive a alegria que tem todo Pierrô ao ver que descobriu sua Colombina</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O carnaval passou, levou a minha rosa,</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Levou minha esperança, levou o amor criança</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F°\">F°</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Levou minha Maria, levou minha alegria</span>\n                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Levou à fantasia, só deixou uma lembrança</span>\n",
